OverHistory.CommentStrikers: Trent Boult TO K L Rahul
OverHistory.NewCommentry: Trent Boult to K L Rahul Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Trent Boult bowling to K L Rahul, yorker ball, pitching on off stump, K L Rahul plays a forward defensive shot WICKET K L Rahul b Trent Boult (Lucknow Super Giants 0 Runs for 1 wickets)
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: An absolute Jaffa from Trent Boult and the Lucknow skipper has to depart! WICKET K L Rahul b Trent Boult (Lucknow Super Giants 0 Runs for 1 wicket). Trent Boult bowling to K L Rahul from round the wicket, pitching on off stump, and swings back in sharply, goes past the bat-pad gap as Rahul tries to work this on the leg side, and the stumps are castled

OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Trent Boult is on fire at the moment, as he picks up his second wicket in two balls! WICKET Krishnappa Gowtham lbw Trent Boult (Lucknow Super Giants 1 Runs for 2 wickets).
